HOCS PROJECT LICENSING OVERVIEW
========================================================================

The HOCS (Hybrid Optical Computing System) project is distributed under a 
multi-license structure to accommodate both its hardware and software components.

1. SOFTWARE LICENSE (Drivers, Python Scripts, Verilog)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
All source code files, including Python drivers, Verilog HDL, and simulation 
scripts, are licensed under the MIT LICENSE.

